25:34.951 --> 25:36.703
- TELL HER I SAID GOOD LUCK.

25:36.703 --> 25:37.787
- WHAT, YOU'RE NOT GONNA
GO BE WITH HER?

25:37.787 --> 25:39.121
- HELL, NO.
I GOT WORK.

25:39.121 --> 25:40.122
- IT'S NOT THE BABY'S FAULT

25:40.122 --> 25:41.290
YOU GUYS ARE A SHIT SHOW.

25:41.290 --> 25:42.333
- YEAH, AND IT'S NOT MY FAULT

25:42.333 --> 25:43.542
THE BITCH GOT KNOCKED UP.

25:43.542 --> 25:45.711
WHO THE FUCK KNOWS IF
IT'S EVEN MINE?

25:45.711 --> 25:49.090
- YOU'RE AN ASSHOLE.

25:49.090 --> 25:51.635
- CONGRATS.

25:51.635 --> 25:53.552
- FULL HOUSE,
LIKE OLD TIMES.

25:53.552 --> 25:55.346
SMELLS GOOD.
LEFTOVERS?

25:55.346 --> 25:56.931
- YOU DESTROYED MY ART PROJECT.

25:56.931 --> 25:58.600
IT'S COMPLETELY RUINED.

25:58.600 --> 26:00.351
YOU'RE SUCH A BITCH!

26:00.351 --> 26:01.352
- WHOA, DEBBIE!

26:01.352 --> 26:02.729
- SHE WENT INTO MY ROOM,

26:02.729 --> 26:04.355
