26:04.355 --> 26:06.107
AND SHE KICKED ALL OF MY CLOTHES
UNDER THE BED.

26:06.107 --> 26:07.817
- I ASKED YOU TO CLEAN UP.
- DID YOU?

26:07.817 --> 26:09.026
- SHE WENT THROUGH MINE TOO.

26:09.026 --> 26:10.319
