TO FIND THAT?

26:14.616 --> 26:16.200
- I TOLD YOU TO GET RID
OF THAT STUFF.

26:16.200 --> 26:18.369
I HID IT SO THE STUPID P.O.
WOULDN'T FIND IT.

26:18.369 --> 26:20.955
- WELL, LUCKILY, YOUR STUPID
SISTER FOUND IT FIRST.

26:20.955 --> 26:24.542
GOD, MAYBE NEXT TIME YOU'LL DO
WHAT I ASK, BOTH OF YOU.

26:24.542 --> 26:26.877
THERE'S MACARONI SALAD
SANDWICHES FOR LUNCH.

26:26.877 --> 26:28.587
EXTRA MAYO.
- DON'T NEED IT.

26:28.587 --> 26:30.715
I'M SUSPENDED.
- WELL, YOU STILL NEED TO EAT.

26:30.715 --> 26:32.216
- LOOK, WE'RE GONNA
GET OUT OF HERE, OKAY?

26:32.216 --> 26:33.592
WE'LL BE BACK FOR DINNER
TONIGHT.

26:33.592 --> 26:35.804
WELL, LIP,
YOU CAN LEAVE LIAM HERE.

26:35.804 --> 26:37.096
- I GOT HIM.
- NO, I--LIP.

26:37.096 --> 26:39.766
- LOOK, FIONA,
JUST GET SOME SLEEP, OKAY?

26:39.766 --> 26:40.975
HANG OUT WITH V.

26:40.975 --> 26:42.893
RELAX, FOR FUCK'S SAKE.

26:42.893 --> 26:45.479
YOU GUYS TEXT ME
IF ANYTHING'S GOING ON, OKAY?

26:45.479 --> 26:47.273
- YEAH, SURE.
COME ON, CARL. LET'S GO.

26:47.273 --> 26:48.817
- WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
- TO SHEILA'S.

26:48.817 --> 26:50.568
- WHY?

26:50.568 --> 26:51.778
- TO SEE IF FRANK CAN TAKE ME
TO SCHOOL TOMORROW MORNING.

26:51.778 --> 26:52.653
- WELL, WHEN WILL YOU BE BACK?

26:52.653 --> 26:53.988
LATER.
GET OFF MY ASS.

26:53.988 --> 26:55.281
- BYE, IAN.

26:55.281 --> 26:58.284
- BYE, DEBS.

27:00.661 --> 27:02.204
- HEY.

27:02.204 --> 27:06.625
WANT SOME MORE?

27:10.004 --> 27:13.674
- YOU GOT ANY CASH
YOU COULD TOSS MY WAY?

27:13.674 --> 27:15.134
- I'M WORKING A DOUBLE TONIGHT.

27:15.134 --> 27:17.136
YOU WANT TO STOP BY?
- YEAH, SURE.

27:17.136 --> 27:19.472
GOT NOTHING BETTER TO DO THAN
WATCH A BUNCH OF PRUNEY QUEENS

27:19.472 --> 27:23.809
SLAP THEIR SACKS
AGAINST YOUR ASS CHEEKS.

27:23.809 --> 27:25.603
- SHIT!

27:26.937 --> 27:29.440
HEY! GUYS!

27:37.865 --> 27:40.659
- HI, UM,
SHEILA LEFT ME A KEY.

27:40.659 --> 27:42.745
- I'M SO GLAD YOU CAME.
WELCOME.

27:42.745 --> 27:44.205
- SUPPOSED TO WATER THE PLANTS.

27:44.205 --> 27:46.207
WHY IS THERE A FOR SALE SIGN
OUT FRONT?

27:46.207 --> 27:48.626
- DAD, DEBBIE AND CARL ARE HERE.

27:48.626 --> 27:50.294
- CAN YOU COME WITH ME
TO SCHOOL TOMORROW MORNING?

27:50.294 --> 27:53.923
- HAVE TO CANCEL MY MORNING
SPIN CLASS.

27:53.923 --> 27:55.257
WHAT'S UP?

27:55.257 --> 27:57.009
- I GOT SUSPENDED
FOR BULLYING.

27:57.009 --> 27:58.260
NEED A PARENT TO COME WITH ME
TO APOLOGIZE.

27:58.260 --> 27:59.678
- APO--[sighs]

27:59.678 --> 28:01.514
OUTRAGEOUS.

28:01.514 --> 28:02.766
FEED ME NUMBING AGENTS

28:02.766 --> 28:03.974
AND DRAG ME TO THE RING.

28:03.974 --> 28:05.768
- YOU ARE IN NO SHAPE
TO GO ANYWHERE.

28:05.768 --> 28:07.937
- HE NEEDS TO
OR ELSE I'LL GET EXPELLED.

28:07.937 --> 28:09.898
- I'M SO SORRY, CARL,
BUT HE'S TOO WEAK.

28:09.898 --> 28:11.065
- [mouthing words]

28:11.065 --> 28:12.776
- COULD I BORROW
A LONG SWEATER?

28:12.776 --> 28:14.693
- OF COURSE, HONEY.
HERE.

28:14.693 --> 28:16.780
- THANKS.

28:16.780 --> 28:17.738
- DO YOU NEED ANYTHING ELSE?

28:17.738 --> 28:20.407
- UM...

28:20.407 --> 28:21.784
- OH, OKAY.

28:21.784 --> 28:24.870
HEY, CARL,
IF YOU GRAB THOSE BALLOONS

28:24.870 --> 28:26.539
AND TIE THEM
TO THE SIGN OUT FRONT,

28:26.539 --> 28:28.916
I'LL LET YOU HOLD MY GUN.

28:28.916 --> 28:31.627
- I GOT MY PERIOD,
BUT ALL FIONA HAS ARE TAMPONS

28:31.627 --> 28:33.880
AND I'M SAVING MY VIRGINITY
UNTIL I BECOME A WOMAN.

28:33.880 --> 28:35.297
- OKAY, FIRST OF ALL,

28:35.297 --> 28:37.884
YOU CAN'T LOSE YOUR VIRGINITY
TO A TAMPON.

28:37.884 --> 28:40.469
IT HAS TO BE A PENIS
WITH A MAN ATTACHED.

28:40.469 --> 28:42.555
AND SECOND,
YOU'RE ALREADY A WOMAN.

28:42.555 --> 28:43.556
OFFICIALLY.

28:43.556 --> 28:44.640
FROM THE MOMENT AUNT FLO

28:44.640 --> 28:46.725
CAME KNOCKING AT YOUR VAGINA.

28:46.725 --> 28:48.352
- THEN WHY WON'T MY BOYFRIEND
HAVE SEX WITH ME

28:48.352 --> 28:49.645
UNTIL I'M 16?

28:49.645 --> 28:50.939
- WOW.

28:50.939 --> 28:52.106
THEY STILL MAKE THEM
LIKE THAT?

28:52.106 --> 28:53.274
YOU GOT A GOOD ONE.

28:53.274 --> 28:55.442
TAMPONS ARE VARSITY LEVEL,

28:55.442 --> 28:56.652
AND YOU ARE STILL J.V.

28:56.652 --> 28:59.530
HERE, TRY THESE.

28:59.530 --> 29:00.948
- THANKS.

29:00.948 --> 29:02.283
COULD I STAY HERE TONIGHT?

29:02.283 --> 29:04.118
- I LOVE A SLEEPOVER.

29:04.118 --> 29:05.870
ABSOLUTELY.

29:05.870 --> 29:08.873
[ukulele music]

29:08.873 --> 29:14.003
♪ ♪

29:14.003 --> 29:16.005
[bracelet beeping]

29:19.884 --> 29:22.052
- [sighs]

29:22.052 --> 29:23.721
HEY, WHAT'S UP?

29:23.721 --> 29:25.932
- UH, LISTEN, I'M TRYING
TO TAKE THE TRASH OUT.

29:25.932 --> 29:27.016
COULD YOU COME HELP?

29:27.016 --> 29:28.642
- SURE.
YOU NEED ANYTHING ELSE?

29:28.642 --> 29:30.352
- HOW ABOUT A GALLON OF VODKA?

29:30.352 --> 29:32.313
- ALL RIGHT, I'LL BE THERE
IN 20 MINUTES.

29:32.313 --> 29:36.692
- THANKS.

29:36.692 --> 29:39.278
- SO WE HAVE LEGOS,
MR. POTATO HEAD,

29:39.278 --> 29:41.280
DINOSAURS, CARS.

29:41.280 --> 29:43.199
MAKE SURE HE EATS
AT LEAST HALF HIS PB&J

29:43.199 --> 29:44.533
BEFORE YOU GIVE HIM
HIS CHEETOS,

29:44.533 --> 29:46.160
AND HE HASN'T POOPED TODAY,

29:46.160 --> 29:48.913
BUT HE'LL USUALLY GRAB HIS BUTT
AND YELL "DOODY BOMB!"

29:48.913 --> 29:50.539
SO YOU'LL HAVE FAIR WARNING.

29:50.539 --> 29:51.540
WHAT ELSE--
OH.

29:51.540 --> 29:52.876
KEEP AN EYE ON HIS CRAYONS.

29:52.876 --> 29:54.627
HE LIKES TO JAM THEM
UP HIS NOSE.

29:54.627 --> 29:56.128
- OKAY, GOT IT.

29:56.128 --> 29:58.422
THIS KID, TOTAL DREAMBOAT.

29:58.422 --> 30:00.424
THE MEN IN MY LIFE
SHOULD BE HALF AS CHARMING.

30:00.424 --> 30:03.344
- OKAY, THEN WE GOT BAND-AIDS,
BUTT WIPES--

30:03.344 --> 30:06.013
OH, STUFFED MONKEY,
OF COURSE.

30:06.013 --> 30:09.016
TWO BOUNCY BALLS,
TWO PUZZLES, VERY HUNGRY HIPPOS,

30:09.016 --> 30:11.602
AND THEN WE'VE GOT A THERMOMETER
AND THEN CHILDREN'S TYLENOL,

30:11.602 --> 30:12.937
YOU KNOW, JUST IN CASE
HE GETS A FEVER.

30:12.937 --> 30:14.772
- OKAY, HOW LONG
ARE YOU GONNA BE GONE FOR?

30:14.772 --> 30:16.607
- OH, THREE HOURS, BUT,
YOU KNOW,

30:16.607 --> 30:19.193
YOU CAN'T BE TOO CAREFUL.

30:19.193 --> 30:20.986
- YOU'RE A REALLY GOOD PERSON.

30:20.986 --> 30:22.989
- NO, IF I WERE
A REALLY GOOD PERSON,

30:22.989 --> 30:26.617
THEN I WOULD QUIT SCHOOL
AND I'D STAY HOME FULL TIME.

30:26.617 --> 30:31.163
- WELL, WHO DOES THAT HELP?

30:31.163 --> 30:32.706
- RIGHT. UM...

30:32.706 --> 30:34.583
OKAY, SO I'LL BE BACK
AT 2:00.

30:34.583 --> 30:36.044
IS THAT STILL COOL?

30:36.044 --> 30:37.503
- DON'T FORGET ABOUT
THE ABC PARTY

30:37.503 --> 30:38.922
TONIGHT AT THE DORM.

30:38.922 --> 30:40.214
- WHAT'S THAT?
- OH, YOU KNOW.

30:40.214 --> 30:41.924
"ANYTHING BUT CLOTHES."

30:41.924 --> 30:45.844
DUCT TAPE, CAUTION TAPE,
TRASH BAGS, BEDSHEETS.

30:45.844 --> 30:48.013
- OKAY, WELL, I GOT A LIT PAPER
DUE TOMORROW,

30:48.013 --> 30:49.682
BUT THAT SOUNDS FUN.

30:49.682 --> 30:51.016
HERE YOU GO.

30:51.016 --> 30:53.769
AND THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR DOING ALL THIS.

30:53.769 --> 30:58.524
YOU KNOW, I WISH I COULD
THINK OF A WAY TO REPAY YOU.

30:58.524 --> 31:01.568
I'M SURE YOU'LL THINK
OF SOMETHING.

31:01.568 --> 31:04.488
[light rock music]

31:04.488 --> 31:07.909
♪ ♪

31:07.909 --> 31:09.702
- HEY. HI.
- HEY.

31:09.702 --> 31:12.038
- SO, UH, I GOT A LAB
AT HALF-PAST,

31:12.038 --> 31:13.122
SO I ONLY GOT,
LIKE, 20 MINUTES.

31:13.122 --> 31:14.873
- THAT'S OKAY.
I'M QUICK.

31:14.873 --> 31:16.542
- RIGHT, AND ALSO

31:16.542 --> 31:18.252
I'M KIND OF GOING THROUGH
SOME SHIT,

31:18.252 --> 31:20.087
SO I'M NOT REALLY LOOKING
FOR ANYTHING TOO, UH--

31:20.087 --> 31:24.341
- DUDE, I'M COLD, I'M HORNY,
LET'S DO THIS.

31:24.341 --> 31:28.637
- OKAY. UH,
SO YOUR LAUNDRY ROOM OR MINE?

31:28.637 --> 31:30.681
- UP AND DOWN,
COME ON!

31:30.681 --> 31:32.308
LET'S BURN THE FAT.

31:32.308 --> 31:33.767
SWING THAT BOOTY!

31:33.767 --> 31:35.269
- WITH FIGURE EIGHT FITNESS,

31:35.269 --> 31:37.896
I LOST A TOTAL 21 POUNDS.

31:37.896 --> 31:40.774
- I'VE LOST 7 1/2 INCHES
AROUND MY WAIST

31:40.774 --> 31:42.944
AND 53 POUNDS.

31:42.944 --> 31:43.945
- I'VE LOST 15--

31:43.945 --> 31:46.990
[frenetic rock music]

31:46.990 --> 31:54.998
♪ ♪

32:00.336 --> 32:02.254
[knocking at door]

32:05.090 --> 32:08.635
[knocking continues]

32:14.016 --> 32:16.060
- THE FUCK ARE YOU DOING HERE?

32:16.060 --> 32:18.980
- I BROUGHT YOU A LITTLE GIFT.

32:18.980 --> 32:21.357
CRONUTS. I STOOD ONLINE
40 MINUTES FOR THOSE.

32:21.357 --> 32:23.025
ONLY LET ME HAVE TWO.
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?

32:23.025 --> 32:26.362
- A TRENDY HYBRID PASTRY
FOR STARTS.

32:26.362 --> 32:28.197
YO.

32:28.197 --> 32:30.491
MIKE TOLD ME.

32:30.491 --> 32:34.578
RIGHT, THE COKE, THE KID,
JAIL.

32:34.578 --> 32:36.789
I CAN'T IMAGINE
WHAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

32:39.583 --> 32:41.835
- I'M STUCK IN
THIS FUCKING HOUSE.

32:41.835 --> 32:45.506
I JUST ORGANIZED CARL'S T-SHIRTS
IN COLOR ORDER.

32:45.506 --> 32:47.133
I'M GOING MENTAL.

32:47.133 --> 32:48.300
CAN'T EVEN MAKE IT
TO THE SIDEWALK

32:48.300 --> 32:50.719
WITHOUT BELLS GOING OFF.

32:50.719 --> 32:52.180
- I, UH--

32:52.180 --> 32:53.680
SO SHOULD I BE EXPECTING

32:53.680 --> 32:56.225
A KNOCK ON MY DOOR?

32:56.225 --> 32:57.226
- WHAT FOR?

32:57.226 --> 32:58.977
- IT WAS MY COKE.

33:00.145 --> 33:02.815
- HEH.

33:02.815 --> 33:04.066
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE HERE,

33:04.066 --> 33:05.734
TO SEE IF I RATTED YOU OUT
TO THE POLICE.

33:05.734 --> 33:07.194
- AND TO CHECK ON YOU--
- FUCK YOU.

33:07.194 --> 33:08.987
- YES OR NO--
- NO, ASSHOLE.

33:08.987 --> 33:10.072
I SHOULD HAVE.

33:10.072 --> 33:11.490
THEY WOULD HAVE LET ME OFF
EASIER.

33:11.490 --> 33:12.741
- WELL, YEAH, WHY DIDN'T YOU?

33:12.741 --> 33:13.992
- 'CAUSE I HATE MYSELF

33:13.992 --> 33:15.119
FOR A NUMBER OF REASONS
RIGHT NOW

33:15.119 --> 33:16.286
AND I'M NOT GOING TO ADD

33:16.286 --> 33:17.371
BEING A SNITCH TO THE LIST.

33:17.371 --> 33:19.206
- [exhales]
OKAY.

33:19.206 --> 33:21.042
- YOU RUINED MY LIFE,
YOU KNOW THAT?

33:21.042 --> 33:22.209
DROPPING THAT LITTLE BOMB
ON MIKE

33:22.209 --> 33:23.210
IN FRONT OF YOUR FAMILY.

33:23.210 --> 33:24.628
- I DID YOU A FAVOR, OKAY?

33:24.628 --> 33:26.380
THE CUP JOB SUCKS

33:26.380 --> 33:29.842
AND MY BROTHER'S A BORING
YUPPIE ASSHOLE, ALL RIGHT?

33:29.842 --> 33:31.177
- HEY, GIRL.

33:31.177 --> 33:32.803
SORRY I TOOK SO LONG.

33:32.803 --> 33:35.055
GOT HELD UP IN THE BATHROOM
BY THE TWO GIRLS IN MY GUT

33:35.055 --> 33:38.058
SITTING ON MY BLADDER
BLOCKING MY FUNCTIONS.

33:38.058 --> 33:39.852
DAMN, YOU LOOK LIKE HELL.

33:39.852 --> 33:41.437
- YEAH, I'M NOT SLEEPING.

33:41.437 --> 33:43.439
- GOOD THING I BROUGHT OVER
SOME SNOOZE JUICE.

33:43.439 --> 33:46.192
- UH-HUH.

33:46.192 --> 33:48.152
- ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

33:48.152 --> 33:50.071
- WE'RE ACCEPTING
CASH ONLY OFFERS

33:50.071 --> 33:51.155
TO EXPEDITE THE SALE,

33:51.155 --> 33:53.282
WHICH IS WHY THE PRICE
IS SO LOW.

33:53.282 --> 33:55.118
OUR LAWYERS WILL HOLD THE MONEY
IN ESCROW.

33:55.118 --> 33:56.243
WE NEED TO UNLOAD IT FAST.

33:56.243 --> 33:57.995
PAYING TWO MORTGAGES
IS KILLING US,

33:57.995 --> 34:01.082
PLUS DAD NEEDS TO GET
TO A WARMER CLIMATE ASAP.

34:01.082 --> 34:02.332
I MEAN, LOOK AT HIM.

34:02.332 --> 34:03.792
- EASY, GRANDPA.

34:03.792 --> 34:05.253
- WE'RE LOOKING TO DO
A RENOVATION,

34:05.253 --> 34:06.170
A FOUR-MONTH TURNAROUND.

34:06.170 --> 34:07.504
WE'LL PURCHASE UNDER ASK.

34:07.504 --> 34:09.006
ALL CASH.

34:09.006 --> 34:10.257
- DUKE IT OUT WITH THE HASIDS.

34:10.257 --> 34:12.217
PUT AN OFFER DOWN
ABOUT 10 MINUTES AGO.

34:12.217 --> 34:14.052
SKINNY DUDES.
YOU COULD PROBABLY TAKE THEM.

34:14.052 --> 34:16.221
- THIS COUCH IS FOR SALE

34:16.221 --> 34:20.976
AND THAT TABLE AND THE TV.

34:20.976 --> 34:22.144
- HOW MUCH FOR THIS CHAIR?

34:22.144 --> 34:23.187
- HOW MUCH YOU WANT TO PAY?

34:23.187 --> 34:24.771
- WELL, HOW ABOUT--

34:24.771 --> 34:28.192
- CASH ONLY.
PLEASE.

34:28.192 --> 34:29.776
DAD, IT'S WORKING.

34:29.776 --> 34:31.069
THEY'RE FALLING FOR IT.

34:31.069 --> 34:32.196
ISN'T THIS FUN?

34:32.196 --> 34:33.489
- YEAH.

34:33.489 --> 34:34.907
- YOU OKAY?
- YEAH.

34:34.907 --> 34:36.283
I'M CONSERVING MY ENERGY

34:36.283 --> 34:37.910
FOR CARL'S THING TOMORROW.

34:43.332 --> 34:45.626
- EVERY GUN'S LOADED, OKAY?

34:45.626 --> 34:51.048
SO HERE WE GOT YOUR BUSHMASTER
XM-15 SEMIAUTOMATIC.

34:51.048 --> 34:54.551
PREMIUM 16-INCH CHROME-LINED
PROFILE BARREL.

34:54.551 --> 34:55.969
- [chuckles]
SWEET.

34:55.969 --> 34:57.471
WHAT DO YOU THINK ABOUT
HOME PROTECTION?

34:57.471 --> 34:59.140
I GOT THREE LITTLE ONES
ON THE WAY.

34:59.140 --> 35:00.974
- SAFEGUARDING
THE OLD HOMESTEAD, HUH?

35:00.974 --> 35:02.559
- HEY, SECOND AMENDMENT,
BROTHER.

35:02.559 --> 35:04.811
GOT TO PROTECT MY FREEDOM
ONE BULLET AT A TIME.

35:04.811 --> 35:06.272
- OKAY, SO...

35:06.272 --> 35:12.069
MILKOR M32 MGL-140
GRENADE LAUNCHER.

35:12.069 --> 35:14.238
PROTECTS A SHITLOAD
OF FREEDOMS.

35:14.238 --> 35:16.949
SIX-ROUND CYLINDER,
DOUBLE-ACTION,

35:16.949 --> 35:18.617
MILITARY GRADE WEAPON.

35:18.617 --> 35:20.118
MISSING A FEW PARTS, BUT...

35:20.118 --> 35:22.163
[chuckling]
IT STILL SHOOTS.

35:22.163 --> 35:23.455
- IT'S HEAVY.

35:23.455 --> 35:24.456
WHAT ARE WE TALKING HERE?

35:24.456 --> 35:25.749
HOW MUCH?

35:25.749 --> 35:27.209
- WELL, AROUND FIVE GRAND.

35:27.209 --> 35:28.502
- $5,000?

35:28.502 --> 35:29.962
- YEAH.
- AW, COME ON, MAN.

35:29.962 --> 35:31.338
[cell phone notification dings]

35:31.338 --> 35:34.342
HOW MUCH FOR THE BAT?

35:34.342 --> 35:36.344
HOLY SHIT.

35:36.344 --> 35:37.427
I GOT TO GO.

35:37.427 --> 35:39.137
HOLY SHIT.
- THAT'S IT?

35:39.137 --> 35:40.931
- CONCIERGE.

35:40.931 --> 35:43.600
MEDICAL CODER.
TRANSCRIPTIONIST?

35:43.600 --> 35:45.353
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT HALF THIS SHIT IS?

35:45.353 --> 35:47.104
- OTHER THAN SUPREMELY BORING?

35:47.104 --> 35:48.146
- [sighs]

35:48.146 --> 35:50.524
NO ONE NEEDS ME ANY MORE, V.

35:50.524 --> 35:52.025
DEBBIE'S DING.

35:52.025 --> 35:54.528
LIP'S IN COLLEGE.

35:54.528 --> 35:56.697
CARL'S IN TROUBLE AT SCHOOL
AND I CAN'T HELP HIM.

35:56.697 --> 35:58.615
WHO KNOWS WHAT'S UP WITH IAN.

35:58.615 --> 36:01.118
- THEY'RE ALL GROWING UP.
WHAT'D YOU EXPECT?

36:01.118 --> 36:04.663
TIME FOR YOU TO FIGURE OUT
YOUR OWN NEEDS.

36:04.663 --> 36:06.415
- TECH SUPPORT PROVIDER.

36:06.415 --> 36:08.125
[scoffs]
UNDERQUALIFIED.

36:08.125 --> 36:09.293
TRANSLATOR.

36:09.293 --> 36:10.836
UNDERQUALIFIED.

36:10.836 --> 36:12.588
THERE'S PORN.
- OVERQUALIFIED.

36:12.588 --> 36:13.589
[both chuckle]

36:13.589 --> 36:15.090
- HEY, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:15.090 --> 36:17.134
- FINDING WAYS TO MAKE MONEY
FROM HOME.

36:17.134 --> 36:18.135
- HUH.

36:18.135 --> 36:20.137
HEY, IS SOMETHING BURNING?

36:20.137 --> 36:21.138
SMELL THAT?
- OH, SHIT.

36:21.138 --> 36:23.015
OH, SHIT!
- SHIT!

36:23.015 --> 36:24.349
- [laughing]

36:24.349 --> 36:26.351
OH, MY GOD.
OH, SHIT.

36:26.351 --> 36:27.352
[smoke alarm beeping]

36:27.352 --> 36:28.604
FIRE IN THE HOLE.

36:28.604 --> 36:29.605
- NOT MY HOLE.

36:29.605 --> 36:32.316
[both laughing]

36:32.316 --> 36:33.900
- YOU JUST LET IT BURN?

36:33.900 --> 36:35.027
- WE GOT DISTRACTED.

36:35.027 --> 36:37.946
OH, GOD.
UGH.

36:37.946 --> 36:39.573
- YOU'RE SHITFACED.

36:39.573 --> 36:42.200
- SINCE WHEN IS IS A FELONY
FOR A GALLAGHER TO DRINK?

36:42.200 --> 36:44.328
- CALM DOWN. IT'S MY FAULT.
I BROUGHT THE VODKA.

36:44.328 --> 36:45.954
- OH, AND POURED IT
DOWN HER THROAT?

36:45.954 --> 36:47.956
- YOU'RE THE ONE WHO TOLD ME
TO RELAX.

36:47.956 --> 36:50.251
SOMEBODY SHUT THAT THING UP!

36:50.251 --> 36:51.668
[smoke alarm continues beeping]

36:51.668 --> 36:53.795
- FUCK.
BURN THE HOUSE DOWN, OKAY?

36:53.795 --> 36:54.963
BURN THE FOOD TOO, YOU KNOW,

36:54.963 --> 36:56.382
I CAN ALWAYS STEAL SOME MORE

36:56.382 --> 36:57.799
FROM MY SHITTY WORK-STUDY JOB,
RIGHT?

36:57.799 --> 36:59.302
- I'M GOING THROUGH SOMETHING
HERE.

36:59.302 --> 37:00.636
- YEAH, IT LOOKS LIKE
YOU WENT THROUGH

37:00.636 --> 37:02.346
ABOUT FIVE BEVERAGES
IN AN HOUR, FIONA.

37:02.346 --> 37:03.805
HAVE ANOTHER ONE.
WHY NOT?

37:03.805 --> 37:06.099
YOU'RE YOUR OWN WOMAN.
RIGHT?

37:06.099 --> 37:08.226
NO, BANG THE BOSS'S BROTHER.

37:08.226 --> 37:10.354
LEAVE COKE OUT ON THE TABLE
FOR THE KIDS.

37:10.354 --> 37:11.314
GET ARRESTED.

37:11.314 --> 37:12.773
DO WHATEVER THE FUCK

37:12.773 --> 37:14.816
YOU NEED TO DO.

37:14.816 --> 37:15.901
I'VE GOT THIS.

37:15.901 --> 37:17.319
HEY, CARL,
GO UPSTAIRS,

37:17.319 --> 37:19.405
GET YOUR TOOTHBRUSH
AND SOMETHING TO SLEEP IN.

37:19.405 --> 37:20.989
- HE HAS THE SUSPENSION MEETING
TOMORROW.

37:20.989 --> 37:22.366
- OH, NO WORRIES.
NO WORRIES.

37:22.366 --> 37:23.450
I'LL GET HIM TO SHEILA'S
IN TIME.

37:23.450 --> 37:24.534
STAY UP ALL NIGHT STUDYING.

37:24.534 --> 37:26.036
I MEAN, WHAT THE FUCK?

37:26.036 --> 37:27.455
IT'S JUST AN APPLIED PHYSICS
QUIZ.

37:27.455 --> 37:28.747
WHERE'S DEBBIE?

37:28.747 --> 37:30.040
- SHE'S AT SHEILA'S
WITH SAMMI.

37:30.040 --> 37:31.583
- VERONICA!
- YEAH?

37:31.583 --> 37:33.085
- YOU'RE NOT ANSWERING
YOUR PHONE?

37:33.085 --> 37:34.461
- I DIDN'T HEAR IT.
WHAT'S UP?

37:34.461 --> 37:35.796
- CAROL.
SHE'S IN LABOR.

37:35.796 --> 37:37.547
- WHAT?
OH, SHIT.

37:37.547 --> 37:38.632
WISH US LUCK.

37:38.632 --> 37:40.592
- THERE'S SOMETHING BURNING.

37:40.592 --> 37:42.386
- LET'S GO. COME ON.
- GO--NO.

37:42.386 --> 37:44.388
HEY, COME ON.
LIP, PLEASE.

37:44.388 --> 37:46.474
YOU DON'T HAVE TO TAKE THEM.
- YOU'RE RIGHT. I DON'T.

37:46.474 --> 37:49.184
COME ON. WHAT ABOUT DINNER?

37:49.184 --> 37:50.478
- ENJOY.

37:50.478 --> 37:54.481
[smoke alarm continues beeping]

37:54.481 --> 37:56.400
- [sighs]

37:56.400 --> 37:59.611
SHUT UP!

37:59.611 --> 38:02.447
[screams]

38:02.447 --> 38:05.409
[ZZ Ward's Move Like U
Stole It]

38:05.409 --> 38:13.375
♪ ♪

38:31.435 --> 38:35.523
- ♪ I WANT YOU IN MY BED
IN A MINUTE FLAT ♪

38:35.523 --> 38:37.315
♪ LET'S HIT THE BACKSEAT
OF YOUR CHERRY CADILLAC ♪

38:37.315 --> 38:39.234
- THOSE FINGERS GO ANYWHERE
NEAR THAT COCK,

38:39.234 --> 38:40.861
I'M GONNA BREAK EVERY KNUCKLE
IN YOUR HAND,

38:40.861 --> 38:42.237
ALL 15 OF THEM.

38:42.237 --> 38:43.864
- SETTLE DOWN, RUMBLE FISH.

38:43.864 --> 38:47.325
ANYWAY, A HAND ONLY HAS
14 KNUCKLES.

38:47.325 --> 38:48.660
- YOU WANT TO FUCKING DIE?

38:48.660 --> 38:50.371
- ♪ DOWN TO THE FIFTH ♪

38:50.371 --> 38:54.458
♪ AND HIT THAT GAS PEDAL
WITH A HELL OF A KICK ♪

38:54.458 --> 38:56.126
- WE GOT INVITED
TO AN AFTER-HOURS

38:56.126 --> 38:58.712
AT THE LOFT OF
ONE OF MY REGULARS.

38:58.712 --> 39:00.589
IT'S FUN.

39:00.589 --> 39:02.090
WHAT'S WRONG WITH FUN?

39:02.090 --> 39:03.884
NOTHING UNLESS IT INVOLVES
SOME FAT FAGGOT

39:03.884 --> 39:05.218
SHOVING HIS HANDS DOWN--

39:05.218 --> 39:07.721
NO--
FUCK.

39:07.721 --> 39:10.307
- ♪ SO LET'S NOT THINK
AND JUST ♪

39:10.307 --> 39:13.810
♪ MOVE LIKE YOU STOLE IT ♪

39:13.810 --> 39:17.481
♪ MOVE
LIKE YOU STOLE IT ♪

39:17.481 --> 39:21.860
♪ MAKE YOUR MOVE ON ME ♪

39:21.860 --> 39:29.868
♪ ♪

39:32.496 --> 39:37.083
♪ MAKE YOUR MOVE ON ME ♪

39:37.083 --> 39:38.919
- I MEAN, I THINK ABOUT HIM
ALL THE TIME.

39:38.919 --> 39:40.588
- MM.

39:40.588 --> 39:42.380
- WHENEVER MY BRAIN PAUSES,
HE JUST SHOWS UP,

39:42.380 --> 39:44.382
EVEN WHEN I DON'T WANT HIM TO.

39:44.382 --> 39:46.468
- WHAT DO YOU THINK ABOUT?

39:46.468 --> 39:49.012
- LIKE, HIS HAIR, HIS EYES,

39:49.012 --> 39:50.347
SOMETIMES JUST HIS NAME.

39:50.347 --> 39:52.433
IS THAT NORMAL?

39:52.433 --> 39:53.683
- ABSOLUTELY.

39:53.683 --> 39:54.810
- BECAUSE MY TWO FRIENDS,
HOLLY AND ELLIE?

39:54.810 --> 39:56.520
- UH-HUH?

39:56.520 --> 39:58.104
- THEY'RE ALWAYS LIKE,
"BOYS ARE STUPID,"

39:58.104 --> 39:59.440
AND THEY ACT LIKE
THEY HATE THEM.

39:59.440 --> 40:00.566
BUT I NEVER FEEL THAT WAY.

40:00.566 --> 40:01.775
- HOW DO YOU FEEL?

40:01.775 --> 40:03.985
- UM, THIS IS WEIRD.

40:03.985 --> 40:05.654
LIKE I WANT TO PROTECT HIM.

40:05.654 --> 40:07.072
IS THAT WEIRD?

40:07.072 --> 40:08.240
- NO, HONEY.

40:08.240 --> 40:10.283
- I ALSO FEEL SICK AND DIZZY.

40:10.283 --> 40:13.829
- MM, THAT'S HOW EVERYONE GETS
WHEN THEY'RE FALLING IN LOVE.

40:13.829 --> 40:15.872
- BUT I THOUGHT IT WAS
SUPPOSED TO FEEL GOOD.

40:15.872 --> 40:19.376
- IT DOES SOMETIMES.

40:19.376 --> 40:21.586
THE GOOD PARTS ARE SO GOOD,
YOU'RE WILLING TO SUFFER

40:21.586 --> 40:25.006
AN UNBELIEVABLE AMOUNT
OF PAIN JUST TO GET TO THEM.

40:25.006 --> 40:27.259
THAT'S WHY I HAVE BEEN MARRIED
THREE TIMES

40:27.259 --> 40:29.010
AND ENGAGED 12.

40:29.010 --> 40:31.096
- BUT WHEN DO THE GOOD PARTS
START?

40:31.096 --> 40:34.057
- WELL, RIGHT NOW IT'S HARD.

40:34.057 --> 40:36.476
HE CHANGED THE RULES
A LITTLE BIT BY DUMPING YOU.

40:36.476 --> 40:37.978
BEST THING TO DO?

40:37.978 --> 40:39.479
ACT LIKE YOU DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

40:39.479 --> 40:41.356
- HOW DO I DO THAT?

40:41.356 --> 40:44.442
- WELL, HANG OUT WITH HIM.
MAKE YOURSELF PRETTY.

40:44.442 --> 40:47.946
GIVE HIM THE OPPORTUNITY
TO CONSIDER WHAT HE GAVE UP.

40:47.946 --> 40:50.657
THAT'S HOW A WOMAN
HANDLES THINGS.

40:50.657 --> 40:52.742
- AND THEN HE'LL WANT ME BACK?

40:52.742 --> 40:54.578
- HAVE TO BE PATIENT.

40:54.578 --> 40:56.454
THIS IS A LONG CON, BABY.

40:56.454 --> 40:57.497
YOU'RE IN IT TO WIN IT.

40:57.497 --> 40:59.124
STAY THE COURSE.

40:59.124 --> 41:00.292
- GOT IT.

41:00.292 --> 41:01.751
THANKS FOR TALKING TO ME.

41:01.751 --> 41:03.670
I CAN'T TALK TO FIONA
ABOUT ANY OF THIS STUFF.

41:03.670 --> 41:05.547
SHE'S A TOTAL SPAZ RIGHT NOW.

41:05.547 --> 41:10.093
BUT ALSO, I THINK
SHE'S AFRAID OF ENDING UP ALONE.

41:10.093 --> 41:12.638
- THAT'S HER SHIT, NOT YOURS.

41:12.638 --> 41:15.140
- ALL DONE.
NEED HELP WIPIN' AND WALKIN'.

41:15.140 --> 41:16.933
- COMING, DAD.

41:16.933 --> 41:20.521
BE RIGHT BACK.

41:20.521 --> 41:24.065
P.S., I LOVE HAVING A SISTER.

41:24.065 --> 41:28.737
- [chuckles]
ME TOO.

41:28.737 --> 41:29.738
[rock music]

41:29.738 --> 41:33.534
[students cheering]

41:33.534 --> 41:37.746
♪ GET LOST IN YOUR EYES ♪

41:37.746 --> 41:42.334
♪ WE CAN LEAVE THE LIGHTS ON,
GIRL ♪

41:42.334 --> 41:47.130
♪ SO I'LL CONTINUE TO GET HIGH ♪

41:47.130 --> 41:51.635
♪ NO TIME FOR SECOND GUESSING ♪

41:51.635 --> 41:53.178
- HEY, KIDDO,
YOU DOING OKAY?

41:53.178 --> 41:55.138
- YEAH,
IS COLLEGE ALWAYS LIKE THIS?

41:55.138 --> 41:57.307
- ASK RON.

41:57.307 --> 41:59.726
- WELL, I DON'T PARTY THAT MUCH,
AND I TRY NOT TO PLAY

41:59.726 --> 42:02.563
MORE THAN EIGHT HOURS
OF MINECRAFT A DAY.

42:02.563 --> 42:04.522
- AND THEN YOU START DOING
BETTER IN SCHOOL?

42:04.522 --> 42:06.149
ALL THIS COULD BE YOURS.

42:06.149 --> 42:07.901
- COLLEGE RULES.

42:07.901 --> 42:15.909
♪ ♪

42:35.011 --> 42:38.181
- [chuckles]
CHECK OUT THESE DIGS.

42:38.181 --> 42:40.558
LOOK AT THAT VIEW.

42:40.558 --> 42:42.645
- WHAT DOES THIS JOKER DO?

42:42.645 --> 42:44.813
- HE'S AN ENGINEER
AND PART-TIME PHOTOGRAPHER.

42:44.813 --> 42:46.732
I THINK HE TOOK
SOME OF THESE PICTURES ACTUALLY.

42:46.732 --> 42:48.525
- OH, YEAH?

42:48.525 --> 42:49.818
WHY'D HE WANT YOU
TO COME HERE THEN, HUH?

42:49.818 --> 42:51.027
- OH, COME ON, NOT EVERYBODY

42:51.027 --> 42:52.862
WANTS SOMETHING
FROM ME, MICK.

42:52.862 --> 42:54.364
- IAN.
- HEY!

42:54.364 --> 42:56.574
- SO HAPPY YOU COULD MAKE IT.
- RYAN.

42:56.574 --> 42:57.951
- OH, GOOD TO BE HERE.
- MMM.

42:57.951 --> 43:01.246
- HEY, THIS IS MICKEY.
- DELIGHTED TO MEET YOU.

43:01.246 --> 43:02.580
UH, COULD I GET
EITHER OF YOU A COCKTAIL?

43:02.580 --> 43:03.957
- YEAH, YOU GOT BEER?

43:03.957 --> 43:05.166
- I'VE GOT SOME CRAFT BREWS,
A STOUT,

43:05.166 --> 43:06.793
IPA, WINTER WHEAT.

43:06.793 --> 43:08.586
- HOW ABOUT BEER?

43:08.586 --> 43:09.963
- [chuckles] RIGHT.

43:09.963 --> 43:11.632
COULD I BE ANY MORE
OF A FAG?

43:11.632 --> 43:12.924
ONE BEER COMING UP.
IAN?

43:12.924 --> 43:17.095
- LET'S SEE WHAT YOU GOT.

43:17.095 --> 43:19.139
- YOU'RE NEW.
HI.

43:19.139 --> 43:21.224
- HEY.

43:21.224 --> 43:22.308
- YOU HERE WITH IAN?

43:22.308 --> 43:23.811
- YEAH.

43:23.811 --> 43:26.396
- HE'S GREAT.

43:26.396 --> 43:28.815
- SO WHAT DO YOU DO
FOR LIVING?

43:28.815 --> 43:32.027
- I RUN BUSINESS.
- WHAT KIND OF BUSINESS?

43:32.027 --> 43:33.403
- HOSPITALITY.

43:33.403 --> 43:36.031
- OH, NICE.
WHAT REALM?

43:36.031 --> 43:37.615
- I'M A PIMP.

43:37.615 --> 43:41.411
- [laughs softly]

43:41.411 --> 43:43.706
WAIT, YOU'RE SERIOUS?

43:43.706 --> 43:45.081
THAT'S INCREDIBLE.

43:45.081 --> 43:46.667
MY DISSERTATION
IS ON TRANSGENDER SEX WORK

43:46.667 --> 43:48.626
AND SYMBOLIC INTERACTIONISM

43:48.626 --> 43:51.046
WITHIN THE FRAMEWORK
OF HUSTLER-CLIENT RELATIONS.

43:51.046 --> 43:52.672
YOU GOT A CARD?

43:52.672 --> 43:55.675
[soft acoustic guitar music]

43:55.675 --> 43:59.804
♪ ♪

43:59.804 --> 44:03.851
- ♪ AND I KNOW THE WORLD
KEEPS SPINNING ♪

44:03.851 --> 44:08.772
- NIGHT, DEBS.

44:08.772 --> 44:12.860
- ♪ AND I KNOW
I'M OUT OF TIME ♪

44:12.860 --> 44:14.819
- NIGHT, FRANK.

44:14.819 --> 44:17.655
MONICA.

44:17.655 --> 44:24.037
- ♪ I KNOW THE WORLD
KEEPS SPINNING ♪

44:24.037 --> 44:25.371
♪ BUT I'LL TAKE ♪

44:25.371 --> 44:26.664
- GOOD NIGHT, FIONA.

44:26.664 --> 44:28.792
- ♪ MY TIME ♪

44:28.792 --> 44:34.882
♪ WITH YOU ♪

44:34.882 --> 44:38.468
- GOOD NIGHT, LIP.
NIGHT, CARL AND IAN.

44:38.468 --> 44:44.432
- ♪ AND I KNOW THE WORLD
KEEPS SPINNING ♪

44:44.432 --> 44:52.232
♪ I KNOW I'M OUT OF TIME ♪

44:52.232 --> 44:53.734
- [sniffs]

44:53.734 --> 44:57.738
- ♪ AND I KNOW THE WORLD
KEEPS SPINNING ♪

44:57.738 --> 44:59.447
- GOOD NIGHT, LIAM.
[sobbing]

44:59.447 --> 45:04.410
- ♪ BUT I'LL TAKE MY TIME ♪

45:04.410 --> 45:09.290
♪ WITH YOU ♪

45:09.290 --> 45:15.756
♪ ♪

45:19.467 --> 45:22.470
[The F String's
Nothing At All]

45:22.470 --> 45:28.476
♪ ♪

45:31.563 --> 45:33.941
- WHOA.

45:55.753 --> 45:58.423
- IT'S TIME.

45:58.423 --> 45:59.800
- OH, SHIT.

45:59.800 --> 46:01.009
TIME TO BE A DADDY.

46:04.721 --> 46:06.014
WAIT, WHAT, WE MISSED IT?

46:06.014 --> 46:07.640
- WHY DIDN'T ANYONE WAKE US?

46:07.640 --> 46:09.517
- I TOLD HER NOT TO.

46:09.517 --> 46:12.645
I NEEDED TO DO THIS
ON MY OWN.

46:12.645 --> 46:13.981
[coos at baby]

46:13.981 --> 46:15.064
- OH, HEY.

46:19.986 --> 46:21.946
HEY.

46:21.946 --> 46:23.698
WHOA.

46:23.698 --> 46:25.366
HE--HE'S--HE'S NOTHING.

46:25.366 --> 46:28.411
HE'S JUST SOFTNESS AND GOO.

46:28.411 --> 46:29.746
HEY, BUDDY.

46:29.746 --> 46:31.497
I'M YOUR DADDY.

46:31.497 --> 46:33.959
AND YOUR BROTHER-IN-LAW.
HOW WEIRD IS THAT?

46:33.959 --> 46:36.753
- YOU KNOW, HE DID THAT
LITTLE THING THAT BABIES DO

46:36.753 --> 46:39.756
WHERE THEY CAN SMELL
THEIR MOMMY'S MILK,

46:39.756 --> 46:43.801
AND HE COULD HEAR MY VOICE
WHEN I WAS TALKING TO HIM.

46:43.801 --> 46:48.056
AND THEN HE LAID UP
ON MY CHEST

46:48.056 --> 46:51.768
AND HE FOUND MY NIPPLE
AND HE TOOK A LITTLE SNACK.

46:51.768 --> 46:53.186
- YOU OKAY, MAMA?

46:53.186 --> 46:54.812
- YOU KNOW, IT'S JUST
A LITTLE EMOTIONAL,

46:54.812 --> 46:55.813
THAT'S ALL.

46:55.813 --> 46:58.608
- DID I TAKE HIM TOO SOON?

46:58.608 --> 46:59.902
HERE YOU GO.

46:59.902 --> 47:02.779
HERE'S GRANDMA.

47:02.779 --> 47:04.072
- OH.

47:04.072 --> 47:07.325
[crying]
OH, HE'S SUCH--

47:07.325 --> 47:09.912
HE'S SUCH A LITTLE ANGEL.

47:09.912 --> 47:12.998
HE'S AN ANGEL
THAT YOU DIDN'T WANT.

47:12.998 --> 47:14.791
- THAT WAS HYPOTHETICAL.

47:14.791 --> 47:16.376
- BUT HE CAME FROM ME.

47:16.376 --> 47:18.795
HE'S PART OF ME.

47:18.795 --> 47:20.046
- JESUS, MAMA.
- [sniffles]

47:20.046 --> 47:21.839
I'M SORRY.
I JUST--

47:21.839 --> 47:24.133
I JUST DIDN'T KNOW
I WAS GONNA FEEL THIS WAY.

47:24.133 --> 47:25.134
[sniffs]

47:25.134 --> 47:27.220
BUT HE'S JUST--

47:27.220 --> 47:28.596
HE'S JUST SO BEAUTIFUL.

47:28.596 --> 47:29.847
- IT'S OKAY, MAMA.

47:29.847 --> 47:32.225
YOU CAN VISIT HIM
ANY TIME YOU WANT TO.

47:32.225 --> 47:34.019
- HE'S A LITTLE ANGEL.

47:34.019 --> 47:35.270
- KEV.

47:35.270 --> 47:36.897
KEVIN.

47:36.897 --> 47:38.856
- HE'S MY LITTLE ANGEL.

47:38.856 --> 47:39.941
- KEV, SHE WANTS TO KEEP HIM.

47:39.941 --> 47:41.401
- SHE CAN'T.

47:41.401 --> 47:42.986
- SHE'S NOT GONNA LET GO
OF THAT BABY.

47:42.986 --> 47:44.570
- WELL, SHE HAS TO.

47:44.570 --> 47:46.239
AFTER EVERYTHING
I'VE BEEN THOUGH WITH HIM,

47:46.239 --> 47:48.157
HE'S MINE, V.
- KEV, THREE BABIES?

47:48.157 --> 47:49.450
- I DON'T CARE.

47:49.450 --> 47:53.496
THAT BOY IS MY SON.

47:53.496 --> 47:55.540
- LOOK AT ME.

47:55.540 --> 47:56.541
HEY.

47:56.541 --> 47:58.334
LOOK AT ME.

47:58.334 --> 48:00.128
THERE CAN BE TWO.

48:00.128 --> 48:03.631
OUR TWO BEAUTIFUL BABY GIRLS.

48:03.631 --> 48:04.967
SHE'S A GOOD MOM.

48:04.967 --> 48:06.259
SHE'LL BE GREAT.

48:06.259 --> 48:08.011
LOOK HOW WELL I TURNED OUT.

48:08.011 --> 48:12.015
- YEAH, WELL,
THE JURY'S STILL OUT ON THAT.

48:12.015 --> 48:14.225
I DON'T WANT TO LOSE HIM, V.

48:14.225 --> 48:16.644
- HE'LL STILL BE RIGHT THERE
WITH MOM.

48:16.644 --> 48:19.063
HE'LL STILL BE YOUR SON.

48:19.063 --> 48:20.064
YOUR BOY.

48:20.064 --> 48:24.402
HER RESPONSIBILITY.

48:24.402 --> 48:28.448
LET HIM GO, BABY.

48:28.448 --> 48:31.451
- [crying]

48:36.289 --> 48:39.292
[phone vibrating]

48:49.427 --> 48:51.096
- YEAH?

48:51.096 --> 48:53.431
- I KNOW YOU DON'T TRUST ME.

48:53.431 --> 48:56.225
I KNOW YOU WANT
TO PUNISH ME,

48:56.225 --> 48:57.643
AND I GET IT.

48:57.643 --> 49:00.146
I WANT TO PUNISH MYSELF.

49:00.146 --> 49:05.234
I HAVE NO WAY TO PROVE MYSELF
TO YOU OR ANYONE.

49:05.234 --> 49:07.154
BUT, CHRIST, LIP, THIS, LIKE,

49:07.154 --> 49:13.409
RELENTLESS PASSIVE AGGRESSIVE
BULLSHIT,

49:13.409 --> 49:17.705
IT'S KILLING ME.

49:17.705 --> 49:21.709
I NEED MY FAMILY BACK, OKAY?

49:24.128 --> 49:27.340
PLEASE?

49:31.886 --> 49:34.931
[jazz music playing softly]

49:34.931 --> 49:42.063
♪ ♪

49:42.063 --> 49:45.150
- WHOA! WHOA.
EASY, KILLER.

49:45.150 --> 49:46.401
I'M TAKING BREAKFAST ORDERS.

49:46.401 --> 49:48.319
SCRAMBLED EGGS, PANCAKES
OR FRENCH TOAST?

49:48.319 --> 49:50.696
- [exhales]
EGGS.

49:50.696 --> 49:52.281
AND WHAT DO YOU THINK
HE'LL WANT?

49:52.281 --> 49:53.950
- HOW THE FUCK
SHOULD I KNOW, MAN?

49:53.950 --> 49:55.201
I'M NOT HIS KEEPER.

49:55.201 --> 49:57.286
- RIGHT.
DIDN'T MEAN TO ASSUME.

49:57.286 --> 50:00.998
SO...DID YOU GUYS
JUST MEET LAST NIGHT,

50:00.998 --> 50:05.294
OR ARE YOU TOGETHER?

50:05.294 --> 50:09.006
- TOGETHER.
- COOL.

50:09.006 --> 50:11.634
YOU'RE A LUCKY DUDE.

50:24.189 --> 50:26.190
- THERE YOU GO.

50:26.190 --> 50:28.067
FRESH AS A DAISY.

50:28.067 --> 50:30.445
YOU LOOK TERRIFIC.

50:30.445 --> 50:34.074
NOW LET'S GO
KNOCK 'EM DEAD.

50:34.074 --> 50:37.493
GOOD MORNING.

50:37.493 --> 50:40.037
- FRANKLY, MR. GALLAGHER,
YOUR SON'S BEHAVIOR

50:40.037 --> 50:41.914
HAS BEEN AMONG
THE MOST EGREGIOUS

50:41.914 --> 50:43.416
I'VE SEEN AT THIS SCHOOL,

50:43.416 --> 50:45.127
AND I'VE BEEN HERE
A LONG TIME.

50:45.127 --> 50:46.502
- DON'T LOOK A DAY OVER 90.

50:46.502 --> 50:47.545
- [snorts]

50:47.545 --> 50:49.213
- HE TERRORIZES THESE STUDENTS

50:49.213 --> 50:52.425
TO THE POINT THAT THEY MOVE
THROUGH MY HALLS IN FEAR.

50:52.425 --> 50:55.095
SCHOOL SHOULD NOT BE
A PALACE OF TERROR.

50:55.095 --> 50:56.888
IT SHOULD BE
A TEMPLE OF LEARNING.

50:56.888 --> 51:00.266
IF CHILDREN DO NOT FEEL SAFE,
HOW CAN THEY LEARN?

51:00.266 --> 51:01.350
- THEY CAN'T.

51:01.350 --> 51:03.561
- SHE'S ASKING ME, CHIPWICH.

51:03.561 --> 51:05.272
- THE ONLY WAY
TO GET THROUGH TO CARL

51:05.272 --> 51:07.440
IS HAVE HIM FACE
THE TRUTH OF WHAT HE'S DONE

51:07.440 --> 51:11.444
AND LET HIM ABSORB IT
IN A MEANINGFUL WAY.

51:11.444 --> 51:13.070
- DO THAT, OKAY?

51:13.070 --> 51:14.197
- HE CAN'T JUST DO IT.

51:14.197 --> 51:16.115
HE NEEDS TO ACTIVELY ENGAGE.

51:16.115 --> 51:18.285
- GOT ANY SUGGESTIONS.
- YEAH.

51:18.285 --> 51:21.245
HE SHOULD APOLOGIZE TO MY KID
AND EVERY OTHER KID HERE.

51:21.245 --> 51:23.206
INDIVIDUALLY.
LIKE HE MEANS IT.

51:23.206 --> 51:26.042
- OH, SPARE US THE WIENER ACT.

51:26.042 --> 51:29.296
BULLYING IS A VITAL PART
OF EVERY ECOSYSTEM.

51:29.296 --> 51:31.464
IT TEACHES KIDS RESILIENCE.

51:31.464 --> 51:33.508
THE WORLD IS A ROUGH PLACE.

51:33.508 --> 51:36.344
BULLYING IS LIKE
GETTING INOCULATED.

51:36.344 --> 51:38.721
IT'S A VACCINE.

51:38.721 --> 51:40.265
AND YOU LITTLE SHIT,
YOU GOT TO LEARN

51:40.265 --> 51:43.142
TO STAY AWAY FROM PEOPLE
LIKE MY SON.

51:43.142 --> 51:44.894
THAT'S WHAT YOU LEARN
WHEN YOU GET

51:44.894 --> 51:47.189
PUNCHED IN THE FACE BY A BULLY.

51:47.189 --> 51:49.815
HOW DO YOU THINK STEVE JOBS
TURNED OUT SO GREAT?

51:49.815 --> 51:50.816
BULLIES.

51:50.816 --> 51:54.153
AND I GUARANTEE JUNIOR HERE

51:54.153 --> 51:56.739
WILL BE GETTING
THE HOTTEST CHICKS WHEN HE'S 30

51:56.739 --> 51:59.534
BECAUSE HE GOT BULLIED TODAY.

51:59.534 --> 52:01.160
YOU WANT YOUR KID TO PEAK NOW?

52:01.160 --> 52:03.412
MY KID WILL BE PICKING UP
ROADSIDE GARBAGE

52:03.412 --> 52:05.206
IN AN ORANGE JUMPSUIT
IN TEN YEARS.

52:05.206 --> 52:09.418
YOUR KID WILL BE IN MED SCHOOL
CURING CANCER AND GETTING LAID.

52:09.418 --> 52:12.297
YOU'RE WELCOME.

52:12.297 --> 52:13.631
- WHAT IF I WANT
TO CURE CANCER?

52:13.631 --> 52:15.508
- BE LUCKY YOU DON'T GET
GONORRHEA

52:15.508 --> 52:16.634
FROM YOUR CELL MATE.

52:16.634 --> 52:18.302
SPOKEN WITH LOVE, SON.

52:18.302 --> 52:20.388
HOME.

52:20.388 --> 52:22.974
- I AM SO PROUD OF YOU, DAD.

52:25.685 --> 52:28.604
[country rock music]

52:28.604 --> 52:30.898
- HEY, HEY,
CONGRATULATIONS, BROTHER.

52:37.113 --> 52:39.241
- WE LOST HIM.

52:39.241 --> 52:41.951
- GOD, HOW?

52:41.951 --> 52:43.828
STILLBIRTH?

52:43.828 --> 52:47.081
- CAROL.

52:47.081 --> 52:49.166
SHE KEPT HIM.

52:49.166 --> 52:50.209
- HE'S NOT DEAD?

52:50.209 --> 52:51.961
- NO.

52:51.961 --> 52:54.256
JUST A LITTLE LESS OURS.

52:54.256 --> 52:56.216
- SORRY TO HEAR THAT, MAN.

52:56.216 --> 52:57.842
BUT, HEY, YOU STILL GOT
TWO ON THE WAY.

52:57.842 --> 53:00.386
- I WAS SUPPOSED TO HAVE FOUR.

53:00.386 --> 53:02.389
I KEEP LOSING BABIES.

53:02.389 --> 53:04.265
I MEAN, WHAT IF THERE WAS
A RUSSIAN SATELLITE

53:04.265 --> 53:06.309
THAT TOOK OUT ALL
THE COMMUNICATION IN THE WORLD

53:06.309 --> 53:07.310
POOF!

53:07.310 --> 53:08.269
TWO MORE BABIES GONE.

53:08.269 --> 53:09.562
OR IF THERE WAS A MUTANT VIRUS

53:09.562 --> 53:11.105
THAT TURNED US ALL
INTO ZOMBIES--

53:11.105 --> 53:12.982
- THAT'S A MOVIE.
- SEVERAL MOVIES.

53:12.982 --> 53:14.942
SO?
IT COULD HAPPEN.

53:14.942 --> 53:16.986
SEE, BABIES CHANGE
YOUR PERSPECTIVE.

53:16.986 --> 53:18.738
THERE'S DANGER
LURKING EVERYWHERE.

53:18.738 --> 53:21.115
NOW, I'M GONNA START
COLLECTING SURVIVAL GEAR.

53:21.115 --> 53:24.952
CANNED GOODS, MEDICAL STUFF,
WALKIE-TALKIES, FLASHLIGHTS.

53:24.952 --> 53:26.246
MY MOTTO?

53:26.246 --> 53:27.788
PREPARE AND PREVENT,

53:27.788 --> 53:30.416
DON'T REPAIR AND REPENT.

53:30.416 --> 53:31.751
- THAT'S MY MOTTO.

53:31.751 --> 53:35.004
- YOU CAN'T OWN A MOTTO,
KERMIT.

53:35.004 --> 53:36.464
[cartoon gunshots]

53:36.464 --> 53:38.174
- GET HIM!
GET HIM.

53:38.174 --> 53:40.092
- OH! HE DISAPPEARED.
WHAT THE HECK?

53:40.092 --> 53:41.844
- HE'LL REGENERATE BEHIND YOU
IN TWO SECONDS.

53:41.844 --> 53:43.387
TURN AROUND.
- OH! OH, NO!

53:43.387 --> 53:44.847
OH, HE BIT ME IN THE BACK.

53:44.847 --> 53:45.848
[groans]

53:45.848 --> 53:47.475
JERKFACE.
- SO RUDE.

53:47.475 --> 53:49.560
- AW, MAN.

53:49.560 --> 53:51.270
YEAH.
[laughs]

53:51.270 --> 53:53.189
- I'M GLAD WE COULD STAY
FRIENDS.

53:53.189 --> 53:55.983
- YEAH.
YEAH, ME TOO.

53:55.983 --> 53:57.610
DO YOU WANT TO GET A PIZZA?
OR...

53:57.610 --> 54:00.196
- I WISH I COULD,
BUT I HAVE A DATE TONIGHT.

54:00.196 --> 54:01.739
GOT TO GO HOME
AND GET CLEANED UP.

54:01.739 --> 54:03.407
- OKAY. YEAH.
YEAH, SURE. NO PROBLEM.

54:03.407 --> 54:04.992
- BUT IT WAS WAS FUN
HANGING OUT.

54:04.992 --> 54:06.327
- YEAH.
- HIGH FIVE.

54:06.327 --> 54:08.371
- [chuckles]

54:08.371 --> 54:09.830
- SEE YOU.
- I'LL SEE YOU.

54:09.830 --> 54:12.833
