You and I]

54:12.833 --> 54:20.841
♪ ♪

54:28.849 --> 54:30.851
- HI.

54:30.851 --> 54:32.186
HI.

54:37.108 --> 54:40.111
THANKS.

54:40.111 --> 54:41.904
- NO PROBLEM.

54:41.904 --> 54:45.825
- ♪ YOU AND I
SCRAPE THE PAVEMENT ♪

54:45.825 --> 54:48.828
