54:59.381 --> 55:01.465
- AND SO WHAT HAVE WE LEARNED?

55:01.465 --> 55:03.968
- BULLYING IS BAD FOR SOCIETY.

55:03.968 --> 55:06.303
IT HURTS PEOPLE
AND MAKES THEM FEEL BAD.

55:06.303 --> 55:08.639
IT MUST BE STOPPED.

55:08.639 --> 55:11.100
- VERY GOOD.

